sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Admin
  participant Ops as Operations Console
  participant Replay as Replay Service
  participant Domain as Domain Events
  participant Kafka
  participant Idem as ProcessedEvent Idempotency
  participant Audit
  Admin->>Ops: Request dry-run replay with reason
  Ops->>Replay: Validate scope and reason
  Replay->>Domain: Load events
  Replay->>Idem: Check duplicate processing
  Replay-->>Ops: Dry-run impact report
  Admin->>Ops: Confirm replay if permitted
  Ops->>Replay: Execute replay
  Replay->>Kafka: Republish selected events
  Replay->>Audit: Record privileged replay action
